headline: Is Lennar (LEN) Pricing Look Stretched After Mixed Returns And Conflicting Valuation Signals?
summary: If you are wondering whether Lennar's share price still matches the underlying value of the business, the key question is how the current market price compares with what the fundamentals suggest. The stock last closed at US$111.84, with returns of 6.4% over the past 30 days, a 7.3% gain year to date, a 14.1% decline over 1 year, and longer term returns of 25.1% over 3 years and 56.0% over 5 years. These mixed returns have kept Lennar in focus for investors who are weighing shorter term...
